      <title>据媒体报道，印尼下任总统将召集部长候选人</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-14/indonesia-s-next-president-calls-up-possible-ministers-media</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据当地电视台报道，印尼当选总统普拉博沃·苏比安托于周一在其官邸召集部长候选人举行会议，他将在本月底举行就职典礼。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-14/indonesia-s-next-president-calls-up-possible-ministers-media</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 14 Oct 2024 08:09:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>新加坡阻止安联与收入保险公司 17 亿美元交易</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-14/singapore-to-stop-1-7-billion-allianz-income-insurance-deal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[新加坡政府将阻止安联保险集团 (Allianz SE) 提出的以 22 亿新元（17 亿美元）收购本土保险公司多数股权的交易，三个月前该交易引发了公众的强烈反对。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-14/singapore-to-stop-1-7-billion-allianz-income-insurance-deal</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 14 Oct 2024 06:05:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度债券遭遇指数纳入以来首次周度资金流出</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-14/indian-bonds-see-first-weekly-outflow-post-global-index-addition</link>
      <description><![CDATA[符合全球债务纳入条件的印度主权债券自被纳入摩根大通新兴市场债券指数以来，首次出现周资金流出。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-14/indian-bonds-see-first-weekly-outflow-post-global-index-addition</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 14 Oct 2024 05:26:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
